  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What is the syllabus of amcat?",
  "response": "The AMCAT (Aspiring Minds Computer Adaptive Test) is an employability assessment test used by various companies for campus placements and hiring. The syllabus for AMCAT typically covers the following sections:\n\n1. **English Language**\n   - Vocabulary\n   - Grammar\n   - Comprehension\n   - Sentence structure\n   - Synonyms/Antonyms\n   - Error spotting\n   - Para jumbles\n\n2. **Quantitative Ability**\n   - Basic mathematics\n   - Algebra\n   - Geometry\n   - Number system\n   - Ratio and proportion\n   - Percentages\n   - Time, speed, and distance\n   - Profit and loss\n   - Permutations and combinations\n   - Probability\n\n3. **Logical Reasoning**\n   - Deductive reasoning\n   - Inductive reasoning\n   - Analytical reasoning\n   - Puzzles\n   - Data sufficiency\n   - Syllogisms\n   - Coding-decoding\n   - Pattern recognition\n\n4. **Aspiring Minds Personality Inventory (AMPI)**\n   - Personality traits assessment\n   - Behavioral tendencies\n\n5. **Domain-specific modules**\n   - Computer Programming (for IT roles)\n     - Data structures and algorithms\n     - Basic programming concepts\n     - Object-oriented programming\n     - Coding questions in languages like C, C++, Java, etc.\n\n   - Mechanical Engineering (for mechanical roles)\n     - Thermodynamics\n     - Fluid mechanics\n     - Manufacturing processes\n     - Heat transfer\n     - Engineering mechanics\n\n   - Electronics and Communication Engineering (for ECE roles)\n     - Digital electronics\n     - Analog electronics\n     - Communication systems\n     - Signal processing\n\n   - Civil Engineering (for civil roles)\n     - Structural engineering\n     - Surveying\n     - Construction materials\n     - Hydraulics\n\n   - Other domain-specific subjects based on the candidate's educational background and the job role they are applying for.\n\n6. **Situational Judgement Test**\n   - Assessing decision-making skills in workplace scenarios\n\nNote that the actual syllabus might vary slightly depending on the specific requirements of the companies using AMCAT for placements. It's advisable to review the latest guidelines and practice tests provided by Aspiring Minds for the most accurate preparation material.",
